(B) It possesses its own proprietary LLM code, enabling it to accurately comprehend user input and generate appropriate replies or responses. It should continuously save its data to a file so that it can remember things.
It should feature a neural network model—specifically, one designed to function entirely without the need for any APIs.

🔷 Now we will create the main command/formation on which this assistant will work.